Frontend File Tree Structure (React + Vite/CRA)

frontend/
│── public/
│    └── index.html             # Root HTML file
│
│── src/
│    │── main.jsx               # Entry point, wraps App with BrowserRouter + Context
│    │── App.jsx                # Main app with routes
│    │── index.css              # Global CSS
│
│    ├── assets/                # Images, icons, logos
│    │    └── logo.png
│
│    ├── api/                   # API service files (Axios calls)
│    │    ├── axiosConfig.js    # Base axios instance with token setup
│    │    ├── authApi.js        # Auth related API (login, signup)
│    │    ├── contestApi.js     # Contest related API (create, join, list)
│    │    ├── paymentApi.js     # Payment related API (Razorpay integration)
│    │    └── userApi.js        # User profile, history
│
│    ├── context/               # Global state management (React Context + useReducer)
│    │    ├── AuthContext.jsx   # Stores logged-in user, token
│    │    ├── ContestContext.jsx# Stores contest list, joined contests
│    │    └── PaymentContext.jsx# Stores payment status / history
│
│    ├── components/            # Reusable UI components
│    │    ├── Navbar.jsx        # Top navigation bar
│    │    ├── Footer.jsx        # Footer
│    │    ├── ProtectedRoute.jsx# PrivateRoute for authenticated pages
│    │    ├── ContestCard.jsx   # Contest info card (entry fee, prize, slots)
│    │    ├── PaymentButton.jsx # Razorpay checkout button
│    │    └── Loader.jsx        # Loading spinner
│
│    ├── pages/                 # Full pages
│    │    ├── Home.jsx          # Landing page with contests list
│    │    ├── Login.jsx         # Login form
│    │    ├── Signup.jsx        # Signup form
│    │    ├── Dashboard.jsx     # User dashboard (my contests, payments, winnings)
│    │    ├── ContestDetails.jsx# Contest details & join button
│    │    ├── PaymentSuccess.jsx# After payment success
│    │    ├── PaymentFailed.jsx # After payment failure
│    │    ├── Profile.jsx       # User profile & settings
│    │    └── AdminPanel.jsx    # (Optional) Admin page for managing contests
│
│    ├── utils/                 # Helper functions
│    │    ├── validators.js     # Form validation (email, password, etc.)
│    │    ├── formatDate.js     # Format dates
│    │    └── authHelper.js     # Save/remove token in localStorage
│
│    └── styles/                # CSS files for pages/components
│         ├── Home.css
│         ├── Login.css
│         ├── Dashboard.css
│         └── ContestDetails.css
│
└── package.json
